                <h5 class="card-title">Shine: The Gospel in Baka</h5>
                <p class="card-text">The road to translating the Baka New Testament was long and difficult, filled with hardships such as civil war, displacement and more. But the Baka translators persevered. Watch the story of God’s faithfulness to the Baka people of South Sudan.</p>
