                <h5 class="card-title">Lasting Transformation Through Scripture</h5>
                <p class="card-text">Jon Hampshire and his family served for years in the Democratic Republic of Congo (DRC). In this video, he discusses what happened after a genocide affected the area. “Lasting transformation,” he says, “doesn’t take place until people’s hearts are transformed by an understanding of what God’s Word says about things like trauma and grace and forgiveness and healing.”</p>
